{"tid":1421660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真「光復香港，時代革命」原意","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:51:12.000Z","uid":131064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8955b3fa2c4ebc8f0d5a560eeb9c00892c35c65","tid":1421660,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rv5su0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRv5su0A.jpg&h=b9e6212a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(2016年新東補選梁天琦選舉經理FB截圖)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原意在此，雖然口號可以自由詮釋，但詮釋前唔該記返天琦當時點諗 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ec5245200a311090f7d480923f9c2a781bd93611","tid":1421660,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"我重以為已經變左同中共乞議席既和理非解釋添"},{"pid":"567b6a38ea1b288c6dd83e6dcc79c1c26d2af0f9","tid":1421660,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791bdb572411e6c0ac2c95ffa5b49923ec94e45a","tid":1421660,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:51:12.000Z","msg":"其中一個方向係<br />\n正名「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n光復香港 = 回復以往繁榮既香港<br />\n方法: 首4大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n<br />\n時代革命=香港體制要改革<br />\n方法: 第五大訴求<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n而唔係林鄭所誤解既港獨<br />\n<br />\n建議之一, 請其他巴打更改<br />\n<br />\n重溫 616, 71, 721 宣言, 文宣請加油, 令我們的行動合理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423473</a>"}]}